Google Play Books\'92 publisher policies focus on quality, spam, and deception, not on \'93AI\'94 by itself.\
Key trigger areas:\
	\'95	Duplicate / near\uc0\u8209 duplicate content\
	\'95	Multiple versions of the same or very similar book, with minimal distinguishing value, are disallowed and can get removed or the account limited.\uc0\u8232 \
	\'95	Misleading metadata\
