AI itself is allowed as long as the result benefits readers and is not deceptive or abusive.\
\
Making AI Books \'93Real\'94 Enough\
To survive at scale, each book needs to look and read like a legitimate niche title, not a spun template.\
Recommended guardrails:\
	\'95	Strong topic differentiation\
	\'95	Define clear series and sub\uc0\u8209 niches (e.g., \'935\u8209 minute breathing exercises\'94, \'93micro\u8209 journals for coders\'94) and ensure each book covers genuinely different angles, formats, or audiences.\
