	\'95	Human pass + light editing\
	\'95	Run a quick QC pass on TOC, intro, one middle chapter, and the conclusion to catch hallucinations, broken lists, or repetition before upload.\
	\'95	No scraped / pirated text\
	\'95	Do not ingest commercial books or blogs as direct training material or prompts; that falls into piracy/plagiarism, which is aggressively acted on when reported.\
