Stagger uploads: 20-50/week, tracking notifications for flags (appeal low-quality rejections with QA proof). Lint AI output for repetition/misinfo, disclose AI narration if audio-involved, and prioritize high-engagement series based on sales data. This scales to 1000+ without mass suspensions.\
